Power and Authority\
\
1. President Trump froze most foreign aid for a 90-day review and moved to fold USAID into the State Department (2025-02-01): By halting tens of billions in aid and curbing USAID\'92s independence, the administration concentrated foreign-assistance power in the executive, weakening a semi-autonomous development arm and its role in supporting democracy and stability abroad.\
\
